Package org.oboedit.gui.components.graphvizViewer Description

Provides the classes needed to generate the Graphviz Viewer. This is a viewer that generates an image of the ontology graph using the Graphviz application. For some documentation on how the classes interact see the image in org.oboedit.gui.components.graphvizViewer.doc-files.GraphvizConfiguration.png There is an editable svg version of this file in the same directory if you wish to make improvements.
